 {"id":"coding_agent_session_search-0go","title":"P7.3 Integration tests for multi-source indexing","description":"# P7.3 Integration tests for multi-source indexing

## Overview
Integration tests that verify the full indexing pipeline handles multiple
sources correctly, including provenance attribution and deduplication.

## Test Cases

### Multi-Source Indexing
```rust
#[tokio::test]
async fn test_index_local_and_remote_sources() {
    let temp_dir = tempdir().unwrap();
    let db = setup_test_db(&temp_dir).await;

    // Create local session fixture
    let local_sessions = create_fixture_sessions(&temp_dir, "local", 5);

    // Create remote session fixture (simulating synced data)
    let remote_sessions = create_fixture_sessions(&temp_dir, "remote/laptop", 3);

    // Index both
    let mut indexer = Indexer::new(&db);
    indexer.add_root(&local_sessions, Provenance::local());
    indexer.add_root(&remote_sessions, Provenance::remote("laptop".into()));
    indexer.index_all().await.unwrap();

    // Verify counts
    let stats = db.get_stats().await.unwrap();
    assert_eq!(stats.total_conversations, 8);
    assert_eq!(stats.local_conversations, 5);
    assert_eq!(stats.remote_conversations, 3);
}

#[tokio::test]
async fn test_search_filters_by_source() {
    // ... setup with mixed sources

    // Search all
    let all_results = searcher.search("test query", None).await.unwrap();
    assert_eq!(all_results.len(), 8);

    // Search local only
    let local_results = searcher.search("test query", Some(SourceFilter::Local)).await.unwrap();
    assert_eq!(local_results.len(), 5);
    assert!(local_results.iter().all(|r| !r.provenance.is_remote()));

    // Search remote only
    let remote_results = searcher.search("test query", Some(SourceFilter::Remote)).await.unwrap();
    assert_eq!(remote_results.len(), 3);
    assert!(remote_results.iter().all(|r| r.provenance.is_remote()));
}
```

### Incremental Indexing
```rust
#[tokio::test]
async fn test_incremental_index_new_remote_source() {
    // Index initial local sessions
    let mut indexer = Indexer::new(&db);
    indexer.add_root(&local_sessions, Provenance::local());
    indexer.index_all().await.unwrap();

    let initial_count = db.conversation_count().await.unwrap();

    // Simulate adding new remote source
    indexer.add_root(&remote_sessions, Provenance::remote("laptop".into()));
    indexer.index_incremental().await.unwrap();

    let final_count = db.conversation_count().await.unwrap();
    assert_eq!(final_count, initial_count + remote_sessions.len());
}
```

## Dependencies
- Requires P2.2 (multi-root indexing)
- Requires P1.3 (provenance in storage)

## Acceptance Criteria
